ygData.messageBody:
Hail All,

Sha'kel Al'methe (Terrew Marr) here and just wanted to greet all the fellow
paladins out there. I do have one question for you high elf paladins out
there, have you completed Tynkale's first quest? Has anyone completed a
quest? I am curious to as what it offers. I know a lot of magic users quests
result special spells.
Well that is all for now, may your swords strike true.

Sha'kel
